"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/662896","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","false","2017-01-13","<p>According to our records, and following consultation with relevant officers, I can confirm that the Foreign and Commonwealth Office has not awarded any contracts to UK-based public relations companies for work in or on Somalia during this Parliament.</p>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood",,"2017-01-13T14:14:33.673Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/662896/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/662896/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/662896/answer",,,,,"16","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","Foreign and Commonwealth Office","2016-12-20","Somalia: Public Relations","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Foreign and Commonwealth Affairs, (a) how many contracts the Government has placed with UK-based public relations companies that include work in or on Somalia and (b) with which companies those contracts have been placed.","false","Biography information for Tom Watson","West Bromwich East","Tom Watson","58596"
