"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/661773","Ministry of Justice","false","2017-01-31","<p>This Government is committed to improving social mobility and extending opportunity so that everyone has the chance to realise their full potential.</p><p>We want to build a legal system which draws from all talents and represents the great vitality and diversity of modern Britain.</p><p>Magistrates are statistically the most diverse group within the judiciary. More than half of all magistrates are women and 10% are from Black, Asian, and minority ethnic (BAME) backgrounds.</p><p>I recognise, however, that more needs to be done to improve diversity including social diversity. As stated in the Government’s response to the Justice Committee’s report into the role of the magistracy, the time is right to carefully consider our approach to recruitment of magistrates, with a particular focus on the Lord Chancellor’s stated aim to increase judicial diversity, so that the magistracy better reflects the society it serves.</p>","North East Hertfordshire","Sir Oliver Heald",,"2017-01-31T16:22:40.05Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/661773/answer","Biography information for Sir Oliver Heald","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/661773/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/661773/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2016-12-19","Magistrates","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, what plans her Department has to increase social diversity among magistrates.","false","Biography information for Dr Dan Poulter","Central Suffolk and North Ipswich","Dr   Poulter","58084"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/661774","Ministry of Justice","false","2017-01-13","<p>We do not hold information on the socio-economic background of magistrates.</p>","North East Hertfordshire","Sir Oliver Heald",,"2017-01-13T15:01:29.47Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/661774/answer","Biography information for Sir Oliver Heald","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/661774/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/661774/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2016-12-19","Magistrates","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, what data her Department holds on the socio-economic background of magistrates.","false","Biography information for Dr Dan Poulter","Central Suffolk and North Ipswich","Dr   Poulter","58085"
